description: EDM Trivia is a fun way to test your knowledge of Electronic Dance Music. You'll enjoy learning some bizarre and interesting facts about the genre. Alexa will ask you a series of questions. Try to pick the correct answer, or just say "I don't know" to hear the answer.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, start e. d. m. trivia
